{
  "id": "22022421557",
  "title": "[Prochot Flow] Verify operation of Prochot Response Power",
  "description": "<em>(Sections with * are mandatory.  You must fill them in, or say &quot;Not Applicable&quot; or &quot;N/A&quot; if you have seriously considered it and determined there's nothing to say.  Remove these instructions and the explanatory text in each section as you fill things in.)</em><br /><br /><h4>Flow *</h4><p>same steps as cbb and imh entry and exit flows but now testing we can manipulate response power to change the ceiling pcode chooses for each domain&nbsp;</p><p id=\"isPasted\">revised flow, 2025 WW46:</p><ul><li>get pf curves for each gv domain</li><li>set each domain tohighest ratio in the curve to ensure throttling at any power and cydyn point</li><li>get response power to determine the intended ceiling</li><li>confirm each domain isbelow that ceiling</li><li>release prochot and confirm freq above the prev ceiling&nbsp;</li><li>additional steps:<ul><li>confirm thermal unlock is set</li><li>if unlocked change response to power to another point&nbsp;</li><li>confirm each gv domain now set its ceiling to that point, with ratios already set to highest ratio on that domains curve it should be visible</li></ul></li></ul><p><s>since simics doesnt model VRs power consumption even inject wont allow expected power response after prochot injected, did verify ratios drop with prochot in both imh and cbb</s></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; font-size: 12.18px;\" id=\"isPasted\"><s>1. before boot inject power into various VRs, otherwise energy_status will read zero, below commands cause power to be ~55W:</s></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px;\"><s>oakstream.mb.mcp0.vccin1-&gt;mbvr_injection_state = 1</s></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px;\"><s>oakstream.mb.mcp0.vccin1-&gt;mbvr_injection_state = TRUE</s></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px;\"><s>oakstream.mb.mcp0.vccin1-&gt;mbvr_iout_inject_val = 100.0</s></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px;\"><s>oakstream.mb.mcp0.vccin1-&gt;mbvr_pin_inject_val = 5.0</s></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px;\"><s>oakstream.mb.mcp0.imh_die1.pmusvid-&gt;svid_tele_pull_interval = 0.01</s></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px;\"><s>oakstream.mb.mcp0.imh_die1.rc_mio_ew-&gt;tele_interval = 0.01</s></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px;\"><s>oakstream.mb.mcp0.imh_die1.rc_mio_ew-&gt;tele_enable = 1</s></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px;\"><s>&nbsp;</s></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px;\"><s>oakstream.mb.mcp0.vccin0-&gt;mbvr_injection_state = TRUE</s></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px;\"><s>oakstream.mb.mcp0.vccin0-&gt;mbvr_iout_inject_val = 5.0</s></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px;\"><s>oakstream.mb.mcp0.vccin0-&gt;mbvr_pin_inject_val = 5.0</s></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px;\"><s>oakstream.mb.mcp0.imh_die0.pmusvid-&gt;svid_tele_pull_interval = 0.01</s></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px;\"><s>oakstream.mb.mcp0.imh_die0.rc_mio_ew-&gt;tele_interval = 0.01</s></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px;\"><s>oakstream.mb.mcp0.imh_die0.rc_mio_ew-&gt;tele_enable = 1</s></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px;\"><s>&nbsp;</s></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px;\"><s>oakstream.mb.mcp0.imh_die0.punit.punit[0]-&gt;disable_sai_checks =TRUE</s></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px;\"><s>script-branch {</s></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px;\"><s>oakstream.mb.mcp0.imh_die0.punit.cpu.bp-wait-for-time 0.02</s></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px;\"><s>oakstream.mb.mcp0.imh_die0.pmusvid-&gt;sb_cr_pmsb_svid_addr_config_SVID_PWRIN_MASK = 0x3</s></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; font-size: 12.18px;\"><span data-teams=\"true\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 1em;\">}</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 1em;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" /></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 1em;\">2. after boot enable bit 22 in power_ctl msr(msr 0x1fc), response power enabled</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; font-size: 12.18px;\"><img data-fr-image-pasted=\"true\" src=\"https://hsdes.intel.com/rest/binary/22020708745\" data-filename=\"image.png\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border-style: none; vertical-align: middle; width: 406px;\" /><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" /></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; font-size: 12.18px;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" /></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; font-size: 12.18px;\">4. check what is minimum package power:</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px;\">punit.ptpcioregs.ptpcioregs.package_power_sku_unit.pwr_unit = 0x3</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px;\"># The actual unit value is calculated by 1 W / Power(2,PWR_UNIT).</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px;\"># The default value of 0011b corresponds to 1/8 W.</p><div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" /></div><div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">simics&gt; @sv.socket0.imh0.fuses.punit.virtual.pmsrvr_ptpcioregs_package_power_sku_pkg_min_pwr_fuse_df</div><div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">0x320</div></div><div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">## Description:</div><div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">## &nbsp; The minimal package power setting allowed for this part. &nbsp;Lower values</div><div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">## &nbsp; will be clamped to this value. &nbsp;The minimum setting is typical (not</div><div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">## &nbsp; guaranteed).</div><div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">## &nbsp; The units for this value are defined in PACKAGE_POWER_SKU_MSR[PWR_UNIT].</div></div><div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" /></div><div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 0);\">min power is 100W</span></div><div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 0);\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" /></span></div><div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">although, msr 0x614 shows min power being&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 0);\">12W</span>:</div><div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">#bits 16-30 are min power</div><div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">rdmsr 0x614</div><div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">0x12024000600118</div><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; font-size: 12.18px;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" /></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; font-size: 12.18px;\">5. get response power, what energy_status_time should be after prochot inject:</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px;\">simics&gt; @sv.socket0.imh0.punit.ptpcfsms.ptpcfsms.prochot_response_power.show()</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px;\">0x000000000000 : lock (63:63) (rw/l) -- Lock until next reset as needed&nbsp;</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px;\">0x000000000000 : rsvd (62:15) (rw/l) -- Reserved</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px;\">0x000000000128 : prochot_response_power (14:00) (rw/l) -- Indicates the pow...</p><div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"># Indicates the power limit that pCode has to maintain while xxPROCHOT is</div><div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"># asserted. Unit = 0.125 W.</div><div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" /></div><div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 0);\">37W is expected power</span></div></div><div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" /></div><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; font-size: 12.18px;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" /></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; font-size: 12.18px;\">6. calc power before prochot, time in unit of 10ns, energy in 61uJ:</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; font-size: 12.18px;\">#read energy_time_status twice to get delta value, value is 55W</p><div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">running&gt; @sv.socket0.imh0.punit.showsearch(&quot;energy_time&quot;,&quot;p&quot;)</div><div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">ptpcfsms.ptpcfsms.package_energy_time_status = 0x28e38571c1cac2e0</div><div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">ptpcfsms.ptpcfsms.package_energy_time_status.time = 0x28e38571</div><div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">ptpcfsms.ptpcfsms.package_energy_time_status.energy = 0xc1cac2e0</div><div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">running&gt; @sv.socket0.imh0.punit.showsearch(&quot;energy_time&quot;,&quot;p&quot;)</div><div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">ptpcfsms.ptpcfsms.package_energy_time_status = 0x39ef12ecc1f31842</div><div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">ptpcfsms.ptpcfsms.package_energy_time_status.time = 0x39ef12ec</div><div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">ptpcfsms.ptpcfsms.package_energy_time_status.energy = 0xc1f31842</div><div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">simics&gt; @0x28e38571*pow(10,8)</div><div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">68599947300000000</div><div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">simics&gt; @0x28e38571/pow(10,8)</div><div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">6.85999473</div><div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">simics&gt; @0x39ef12ec/pow(10,8)</div><div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">9.7196926</div><div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">simics&gt; @0xc1cac2e0*1/pow(2,14)</div><div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">198443.044921875</div><div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">simics&gt; @0xc1f31842*1/pow(2,14)</div><div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">198604.3790283203</div><div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">simics&gt; @198604.3790283203-198443.044921875</div><div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">161.3341064453125</div><div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">simics&gt; @9.7196926-6.85999473</div><div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">2.8596978699999998</div><div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">simics&gt; @161.3341064453125/2.8596978699999998</div><div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 0);\">56.41648655887991</span></div></div><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; font-size: 12.18px;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" /></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; font-size: 12.18px;\">7. inject prochot,&nbsp;oakstream.mb.mcp0.imh_die0.punit.punit[0]-&gt;prochot_trigger</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; font-size: 12.18px;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" /></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; font-size: 12.18px;\">8. confirm prochot logged:&nbsp;</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px;\">punit.throttle.package_therm_status.prochot_log = 0x1</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px;\">punit.throttle.package_therm_status.prochot_status = 0x1</p><div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" /></div><div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">9. calc new power consumption:</div><div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 12.18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">running&gt; @sv.socket0.imh0.punit.showsearch(&quot;energy_time&quot;,&quot;p&quot;)</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 12.18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">ptpcfsms.ptpcfsms.package_energy_time_status = 0xae5079f4c31298a0</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 12.18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">ptpcfsms.ptpcfsms.package_energy_time_status.time = 0xae5079f4</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 12.18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">ptpcfsms.ptpcfsms.package_energy_time_status.energy = 0xc31298a0</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 12.18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">[oakstream.mb.mcp0.cbb_die2.punit.punit[0] spec-viol] Config register access must contain a 16-bit address</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 12.18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">simics&gt; @0xab2788c1*pow(10,8)</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 12.18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">287149484900000000</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 12.18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">simics&gt; @0xab2788c1/pow(10,8)</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 12.18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">28.71494849</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 12.18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">simics&gt; @0xae5079f4/pow(10,8)</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: